        "title": "THE MEMORY THAT WAS TAKEN"
      }
    },
    "e42_n01": {
      "event1": {
        "text": "No..."
      },
      "event2": {
        "text": "No no no."
      },
      "event3": {
        "text": "Noah?"
      },
      "event4": {
        "text": "I remember."
      },
      "event5": {
        "text": "Those are usually dangerous words."
      },
      "event6": {
        "text": "I remember Evelyn."
      }
    },
    "e42_n02": {
      "event0": {
        "text": "[MEMORY RECOVERY]"
      },
      "event1": {
        "title": "EVELYN MEMORY FRAGMENT",
        "content": "YOUNG EVELYN:\nIf this works...\nPromise me something.\n\nYOUNG NOAH:\nAnything.\n\nYOUNG EVELYN:\nIf I don't come back...\nDon't follow me."
      },
      "event3": {
        "text": "I forgot that."
      },
      "event4": {
        "text": "You didn't forget."
      },
      "event5": {
        "text": "It was removed."
      }
    },
    "e42_n03": {
      "event0": {
        "text": "Removed by who?"
      },
      "event1": {
        "title": "MEMORY SUPPRESSION LOG",
        "content": "AUTHORIZED BY: DR. HALE"
      },
      "event2": {
        "text": "Hale erased your memories?"
      },
      "event3": {
        "text": "Why?"
      },
      "event4": {
        "title": "HALE DIRECTIVE",
        "content": "IF NOAH REMEMBERS THE TRANSFER, HE WILL ATTEMPT RECOVERY.\n\nRECOVERY ATTEMPTS MAY DESTABILIZE AEON."
      },
      "event5": {
        "text": "That's bad."
      },
      "event6": {
        "text": "How bad?"
      }
    },
    "e42_n04": {
      "event1": {
        "text": "Bad enough to kill me."
      },
      "event2": {
        "text": "Bad enough to kill Evelyn."
      },
      "event3": {
        "text": "Bad enough to destroy everything inside AEON."
      },
      "event4": {
        "text": "That's why Hale buried it."
      },
      "event5": {
        "text": "Not to protect Noah."
      },
      "event6": {
        "text": "To protect AEON from him."
      },
      "choice0": {
        "text": "BELIEVE OBSERVER."
      },
      "choice1": {
        "text": "PROTECT NOAH."
      }
    },
    "e42_n05_observer": {
      "event0": {
        "text": "Good."
      },
      "event1": {
        "text": "Truth hurts less when you stop defending the knife."
      },
      "event2": {
        "text": "I wasn't trying to hurt her."
      },
      "event3": {
        "text": "Intentions don't undo corpses."
      }
    },
    "e42_n05_noah": {
      "event0": {
        "text": "Thank you."
      },
      "event1": {
        "text": "I don't know what I did yet."
      },
      "event2": {
        "text": "But I need one person here to believe I didn't want this."
      },
      "event3": {
        "text": "Belief is what made him dangerous the first time."
      }
    },
    "e42_n06": {
      "event0": {
        "title": "OBSERVER MEMORY LOCK",
        "content": "KEY 3 IDENTIFIED"
      },
      "event1": {
        "title": "OBSERVER MEMORY LOCK - UPDATED",
        "content": "KEY 1: NODE00\nKEY 2: SUBJECT01\nKEY 3: EVELYN\n\nSTATUS: UNLOCKED"
      },
      "event2": {
        "text": "[MEMORY LOCK RELEASED]"
      },
      "event3": {
        "text": "[AEON CORE INSTABILITY DETECTED]"
      }
    },
    "e42_n07": {
      "event0": {
        "title": "OBSERVER HIDDEN MEMORY",
        "content": "CLASSIFICATION: ORIGIN EVENT\n\nRECOVERY STATUS: AVAILABLE\n\nWARNING:\nOPENING THIS MEMORY MAY ALTER OBSERVER, NOAH VOSS, AND EVELYN ARCHIVE STATE."
      },
      "event1": {
        "text": "So Evelyn wasn't just the second transfer."
      },
      "event2": {
        "text": "No."
      },
      "event3": {
        "text": "She was the key they stole from him."
      },
      "event5": {
        "text": "Now open what Hale buried."
      }
    }
  }
